quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"Ini: \"ippuweêêa yi d, ar agraw n leonun ssemêessen, u nnan: ih, nesla i Leqwôan, d lwehma"
  72,2,"Inehhu ar ûûwab, d$a numen yis. I Mass nne$, ur nepcarak yiwen"
  72,3,"U Neppa, gedha s loeôs n Mass nne$ Aâlayan, ur Isâi tameddakwelt, ne$ ùùmmi S"
  72,4,"Ih, abuhal nne$ iêekku, af Öebbi, ixmiôen"
  72,5,"Nekwni nenwa leonun akked imdanen, ur sawalen, af Öebbi, tikerkas, d awez$i"
  72,6,"Ih, seg imdanen, llan irgazen ijjemen ddkeô n leonun. Snernan lbe$wv nnsen"
  72,7,"S tidep, $ilen, akken t$ilem, ar Öebbi ur d Isskar yiwen, d awez$i"
  72,8,"Aql a$ nqelleb igenni, nufa t iççuô d iâssasen uqsiêen, akked ijujaê"
  72,9,"Nella nep$imi $uôes, seg imukan nessemêas; win issemêessen tura, a t id immager usafu d aâessas"
  72,10,"Nekwni, ur neéôi ma iura lhemm, af at ddunit, ne$ ma Ib$a, Mass nnsen, ad pwanhun"
  72,11,"Llan garane$ iâaôviyen, llan wid ur nemâin; ur naâdil iberdan"
  72,12,"Nmeyyez nufa, war ccekk, ur nesfunnug Öebbi di tmurt, ur T nesfunnug ma nerwel"
  72,13,"Nnhaya mi s nesla, yis numen. Win iumnen s Mass is, ur ippagwad ara t ixaûen, ne$ ara t ivuôôen"
  72,14,"Ih, garane$ imvuâen, garane$ lâaûûap. Wid iunzen, widak, xtaôen lewqam"
  72,15,"Ma d lâaûûap, di Loahennama, d nitni ay d is$aôen"
  72,16,"Lemmer deg ubrid ay ddan, yili Nefka yasen aman iqwan"
  72,17,"A ten njeôôeb yissen. Win iooan asmekti n Mass is, ad isâaddi aâaqeb aqesêan"
  72,18,Leowamaâ n Öebbi. Ur naâôet yiwen ar tama n Öebbi
  72,19,"Atan, mi ikker umdan n Öebbi ad inuj $ureS, qôib lesqen $uôes"
  72,20,"Ini: \"pnuju$ kan ar Mass iw, ur aS pcarake$ yiwen"
  72,21,"Ini: \"nek, ur pwakelfe$ $ef vveôô nnwen ne$ $ef nnhaya nnwen"
  72,22,"Ini: \"nek, ur iyi ipfukku yiwen seg ufus n Öebbi, d awez$i. War Neppa, ur ppafe$ ssôan"
  72,23,"siwa anabi s$uô Öebbi, akked tebrap iS\". Ih, i wid iâuûan Öebbi akked Umazan iS, times n Loahennama, ad wekkôen degs, i lebda"
  72,24,"Alamma mi walan ayen i sen ippuwaââden, ad éôen anwi ay d uôhifen mavi, i leslak, anwi drus iten mavi"
  72,25,"Ini: \"ur éôi$ ma iqeôb ed wayen i wen ippuweââden, ne$ ma a t Iweooel Mass iw"
  72,26,"Amusnaw n tbavnit; tabavnit iS, ur p Immal i yiwen"
  72,27,"Kkes ed win Iôuva d amazan. Winna, iteddu, zdat deffir, s iâssasen"
  72,28,"Ad Iéeô ma ssawven tibratin n Mass nnsen. Izzi i wayen akw illan $uôsen, Iêeppeb yal cci s imvanen"
  73,1,A win isburen
  73,2,"Aâwez, xas cwiî"
  73,3,"Azgen n yiv, ne$ ssenqes segs, acemma"
  73,4,Ne$ rnu yas. Di Leqwôan ûûun leqôaya
  73,5,"Aql a£, ad ak d Nini awal amray"
  73,6,"Ccaw n yiv, iééaéay kteô asurif, u issewqam kteô leqôaya"
  73,7,"Deg wass, s tidep, tce$wlev, maççi d kra"
  73,8,"Mmekti d isem n Mass ik, lhu yideS, akken iwata"
  73,9,"Mass ugmuv akked utaram, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Ihi, sâu T d Awkil"
  73,10,"Eûbeô i innan nnsen, faôeq iten s leêdaqa"
  73,11,"Eoo iyI inekkaôen, akked usâiyen; efk asen cwiî n lmudda"
  73,12,"£uône£, s tidep, slasel akked tmes iôeqqen"
  73,13,"lqut ipceôôiqen, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  73,14,"Ass ideg tamurt akked idurar ad rgagin, idurar ad u$alen am ôômel ippazalen"
  73,15,"Atan Nuzen awen ed Amazan, d anagi nnwen, akken Nuzen amazan i Ferâun"
  73,16,Ferâun iâuûa amazan. Newwet it tiyta tuqsiêt
  73,17,"Amek ara têezzbem, ma tnekkôem ass ideg igwerdan ad caben"
  73,18,"Segs, ad icerreg igenni, ad iûaô wayen i wen Iwaââed"
  73,19,Atan wagi d asmekti; win iôe$ben ad iawi abrid ar Mass is